# Frontend Architecture

## Structure
```
frontend/
├── app/
│   ├── page.tsx         # Main landing page
│   ├── generate/        # Idea generation flow
│   └── optimize/        # Video optimization flow
├── components/
│   ├── ui/              # ShadCN components
│   ├── forms/
│   │   ├── IdeaForm.tsx
│   │   └── VideoUpload.tsx
│   ├── results/
│   │   ├── ContentIdea.tsx
│   │   └── OptimizationResults.tsx
│   └── shared/
│       └── ViralContentCard.tsx
├── lib/
│   ├── api-client.ts    # Backend API calls
│   └── websocket.ts     # Real-time updates
└── types/
    └── api.ts           # TypeScript API types
```

## UI Flow
1. Landing: Choose "Generate Idea" or "Optimize Video"
2. Platform Selection: TikTok, Instagram, LinkedIn, Twitter
3. Input: Text prompt OR video upload
4. Processing: Real-time WebSocket updates
5. Results: Structure + captions + hashtags + similar viral content

## Patterns
• Functional components with hooks only
• ShadCN for consistent UI components
• Real-time updates via WebSocket connection
